metadata.name: Sudden Voyage to Forever
metadata.description:
in the dream you see god shaking in silence
the enormous monster eyes swing ‘round and ‘round
yet then it’s your face, your eyes, 
you feel a burning knot in its heart
because it’s becoming your heart,
now you’re the one twitching on the ground
and the one watching yourself twitch on the ground 
at both dreams’ ends in silence
until years later one of you laughs 
and finally you wake 
and then it’s the end of time
and that real waiting game begins

"Sudden Voyage to Forever" - September 2022. 
Created by William M. Peaster.
